i.pagesperso-orange.fr/ Official website JM SAVELLI]\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Savelli, Jean-Marc}}\n[[Category:1955 births]]\n[[Category:French classical pianists]]\n[[Category:French male pianists]]\n[[Category:Conservatoire de Paris alumni]]\n[[Category:People from Mulhouse]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:21st-century classical pianists]]\n[[Category:21st-century French male musicians]]\n", "name_user": "Caroledugraindelorge", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean-Marc_Savelli"}
